  <brief_title>Evaluation of an &quot;Opt-Out&quot; Inpatient Smoking Cessation Service on Smoking Behavior Study #1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dissemination of an Inpatient Smoking Cessation Program to South Carolina Hospitals Study #1</official_title>
